    <div class="s-head"><div class="section-icon section-icon--gold rv-scale">🛡️</div><div class="s-tag" style="color:var(--gold)">SKIN BIOLOGY</div><h2 class="s-title">Your Skin Barrier Is Thinning —<br>And Your Water Is Making It Worse</h2></div>
